name: Extravagamt- 8"x10" Print
description:
​Fine art print of one of my original color pastel paintings, with some added digital alterations. Note, this is not the original artwork, but a print of it. It makes a great present for fashionistas and bag lovers!

The dimensions are 8 inches by 10, however, if you are interested in a different size please contact me to set up an arrangement.​

Printed on cold pressed, 100% cotton, acid free, archival paper. It is not framed, but can easily be slipped into one.

The back is signed and dated on the day of purchase. It will be shipped safely as to prevent damage.​

Item is shipped within a week of purchase.
